termios - used to get/set terminal attributes
fcntl   - defines various flags
signal  - used for SIGPIPE handling
unistd  - read, write, pipe, etc
errno   - error message formating 
string  - error message formating 
getopt  - option handling 
poll    - used for checking between parent/child process

